1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:01,811
1.
2
00:00:02,080 --> 00:00:03,650
Be an activationist.
3
00:00:03,841 --> 00:00:05,730
Be someone who does things.
4
00:00:05,920 --> 00:00:08,451
Be a doer, not a don'ter.
5
00:00:09,440 --> 00:00:10,051
2.
6
00:00:10,321 --> 00:00:12,931
Don't wait until conditions are perfect.
7
00:00:13,040 --> 00:00:14,371
They never will be.
8
00:00:14,640 --> 00:00:19,891
Expect future obstacles and difficulties, and solve them as they arise.
9
00:00:20,080 --> 00:00:21,571
3.
10
00:00:21,761 --> 00:00:25,331
Remember, ideas alone won't bring success.
11
00:00:25,600 --> 00:00:29,170
Ideas have value only when you act upon them.
12
00:00:30,400 --> 00:00:34,851
Four, use action to cure fear and gain confidence.
13
00:00:35,040 --> 00:00:38,051
Do what you fear and fear disappears.
14
00:00:38,160 --> 00:00:39,891
Just try it and see.
15
00:00:41,040 --> 00:00:44,770
Five, start your mental engine mechanically.
16
00:00:44,880 --> 00:00:47,331
Don't wait for the spirit to move you.
17
00:00:47,520 --> 00:00:51,491
Take action, dig in, and you move the spirit.
18
00:00:51,491 --> 00:00:53,331
6.
19
00:00:53,680 --> 00:00:55,650
Think in terms of now.
20
00:00:55,920 --> 00:01:02,851
Tomorrow, next week, later, and similar words often are synonymous with the failure word, never.
21
00:01:03,200 --> 00:01:07,011
Be an, I'm starting right now, kind of person.
22
00:01:07,011 --> 00:01:08,690
7.
23
00:01:08,880 --> 00:01:11,250
Get down to business, pronto.
24
00:01:11,281 --> 00:01:13,730
Don't waste time getting ready to act.
25
00:01:13,841 --> 00:01:15,730
Start acting instead.
26
00:01:16,720 --> 00:01:17,331
8.
27
00:01:17,520 --> 00:01:19,011
Seize the initiative.
28
00:01:19,120 --> 00:01:20,451
Be a crusader.
29
00:01:20,560 --> 00:01:22,291
Pick up the ball and run.
30
00:01:22,480 --> 00:01:23,730
Be a volunteer.
31
00:01:24,000 --> 00:01:27,650
Show that you have ability and ambition to do.
32
00:01:28,720 --> 00:01:31,491
Get in gear and go.
